        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Valid in both TWL (Tournament Word List) and SOWPODS (Collins Scrabble Words). PE is the Hebrew letter representing the /p/ or /f/ sound. It joins several other Hebrew letter names (HE, EF, NUN) as valid Scrabble words.</p>
      </div>

